---
/**
 * About / Story section.
 * Large statement text with brand green highlights.
 * Content extracted from the "Who Are We" section of the Flutter app.
 */
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <!-- Pill label -->
      <span
        class="inline-block rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase"
        style="background: var(--surface); color: var(--text-secondary);"
      >
        Our story
      </span>

      <!-- Large statement -->
      <h2
        class="mt-8 text-xl font-light leading-relaxed sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl"
        style="color: var(--text-primary); letter-spacing: -0.4px; line-height: 1.5;"
      >
        We are a community of
        <span class="font-semibold text-[var(--tag-green)]">young, curious travelers</span>
        with a thirst for adrenaline. We created an app that goes beyond typical travel guides.
      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-6 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
        style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;"
      >
        Surfing on deserted beaches, impressive cliff jumps, remote waterfalls,
        excursions only locals know about, magical spots to watch the sunset —
        all this and much more, with real videos, exact locations and visual routes
        on the map.
      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-4 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
        style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;"
      >
        We started this project because we knew there were
        <span class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--text-primary);">incredible spots that deserved to be discovered</span>,
        but were difficult to find. Our mission is to change that.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats strip -->
    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-4xl grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-4"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-[var(--radius-brand)] p-5"
        style="background: var(--surface);"
      >
        <span class="text-2xl font-semibold sm:text-3xl" style="color: var(--tag-green);">11</span>
        <span class="mt-1 text-xs font-light" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Spot Types</span>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-[var(--radius-brand)] p-5"
        style="background: var(--surface);"
      >
        <span class="text-2xl font-semibold sm:text-3xl" style="color: var(--tag-green);">3</span>
        <span class="mt-1 text-xs font-light" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Platforms</span>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-[var(--radius-brand)] p-5"
        style="background: var(--surface);"
      >
        <span class="text-2xl font-semibold sm:text-3xl" style="color: var(--tag-green);">2</span>
        <span class="mt-1 text-xs font-light" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Languages</span>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-[var(--radius-brand)] p-5"
        style="background: var(--surface);"
      >
        <span class="text-2xl font-semibold sm:text-3xl" style="color: var(--tag-green);">&infin;</span>
        <span class="mt-1 text-xs font-light" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Adventures</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
